{"tid":587332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋茨：幾可肯定有另一個08年金融風暴出現！","createTime":"2018-03-10T10:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T11:40:05.000Z","uid":122856,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"67f9a42cc870e23cb189eb1572c728c350f3365b","tid":587332,"uid":122856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"2008年的金融危機引致大衰退和880萬美國人失業，即使用了多年令經濟重上正軌，但很多美國人仍然未能回復金融危機之前的狀態。微軟創辦人比爾&bull;蓋茨（Bill Gates）在論壇表示好肯定，還有另一個如2008年金融風暴的經濟危機將會出現，並說「為時不遠」。<br />\n<br />\n蓋茨上周參與美國Reddit論壇Ask Me Anything的環節，表示很難說出確實是什麼時候出現，但幾可肯定會再次遭遇危機，而幸運的是大家已經完整地經歷過一次。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他透露和股神畢菲特，傾談了很多這方面的問題，他形容畢菲特懂的遠比他多。除了上述擔憂，他表示自己和畢菲特對美國經濟，仍然持樂觀的態度，又指雖然未來可能有巨大的衝擊，但他很樂觀地看到創新和資本主義將如何改善人類的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180309/20326906\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20326906&d=B7r3kp66hFYsc1qTru7AOTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=b9a529a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20326906&h=7d99483a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20180309/20326906</a>"},{"pid":"e80e7fd214ecd5934dace83b60fc7ba8c6c27a45","tid":587332,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"191cbe355018a876c66c7bd2cd4769177d94e609","tid":587332,"uid":81150,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:26:41.000Z","msg":"蓋茨呃尻我   屌你老母"},{"pid":"ac0c31489f6d16951501a92e3d3bd78748914fb6","tid":587332,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:27:49.000Z","msg":"係咪下半年呀"},{"pid":"251b6f8b16b3bc043904775949d939e3d1e6ffeb","tid":587332,"uid":138420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T11:29:23